## Source auth patterns (reference)

| Pattern | Sources | How token is obtained |
|---------|---------|----------------------|
| Bearer OAuth | asana, slack, google_drive, hubspot, airtable, zendesk, sharepoint_online, notion, linear, jira | `get_access_token()` → TokenProvider |
| Bearer API key | attio, slab | `self.api_key` (static, no refresh) |
| `token` header (PAT) | github | `self.personal_access_token` |
| NTLM | sharepoint2019v2 | username/password/domain from auth config |
| Cross-resource | sharepoint_online | `get_token_for_resource(scope)` on OAuthTokenProvider |
